Package: Nebulosa
Type: Package
Title: Single-Cell Data Visualisation Using Kernel Gene-Weighted Density Estimation
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(person("Jose", "Alquicira-Hernandez", email = "alquicirajose@gmail.com",
        role = c("aut", "cre"), comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-9049-7780")))
Description: This package provides a enhanced visualization of single-cell gene expression based on gene-weighted density estimation, particularly for recovering the signal from dropped-out genes and inspecting the combined expression from a set of genes.
